\c 11
\s UJefitha ukhulula abantwana bakoIsrayeli kumaAmoni
\p
\v 1 Njalo uJefitha umGileyadi wayeliqhawe elilamandla\x + 6.12. 2 Kho. 5.1.\x*, wayeyindodana yewule; uGileyadi wasezala uJefitha.
\v 2 UmkaGileyadi wasemzalela amadodana; kwathi amadodana omkakhe esekhulile amxotsha uJefitha, athi kuye: Kawuyikudla ilifa endlini kababa, ngoba uyindodana yomunye umfazi.
\v 3 UJefitha wasebalekela abafowabo, wahlala elizweni leTobi\x + 11.5. 2 Sam. 10.6,8.\x*. Amadoda ayize asebuthana kuJefitha, aphuma laye\x + 9.4. 1 Sam. 22.2.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Kwasekusithi emva kwezinsuku abantwana bakoAmoni balwa loIsrayeli.
\v 5 Kwasekusithi lapho abantwana bakoAmoni besilwa loIsrayeli, abadala beGileyadi bahamba ukuyathatha uJefitha elizweni leTobi,
\v 6 bathi kuJefitha: Woza ube ngumkhokheli wethu ukuze silwe labantwana bakoAmoni.
\v 7 Kodwa uJefitha wathi kubadala beGileyadi: Lina kalingizondanga yini, langixotsha endlini kababa? Pho, lizelani kimi khathesi nxa selisenhluphekweni\x + Gen. 26.27.\x*?
\v 8 Abadala beGileyadi basebesithi kuJefitha: Ngakho khathesi siyabuyela kuwe ukuze uhambe lathi uyekulwa umelene labantwana bakoAmoni, ube yinhloko yethu phezu kwabo bonke abakhi beGileyadi\x + 10.18.\x*.
\v 9 UJefitha wasesithi kubadala beGileyadi: Uba lingibuyisa ukulwa ngimelene labantwana bakoAmoni, iN\nd kosi\nd* ibanikele phambi kwami, mina ngizakuba yinhloko yenu yini?
\v 10 Abadala beGileyadi basebesithi kuJefitha: IN\nd kosi\nd* iyezwa phakathi kwethu, uba singenzi njalo njengokwamazwi akho\x + Jer. 42.5.\x*.
\v 11 UJefitha wasehamba labadala beGileyadi, abantu basebemenza waba yinhloko lomkhokheli phezu kwabo\x + 11.6,8.\x*. UJefitha wasekhuluma wonke amazwi akhe phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 20.1. 1 Sam. 10.19,25. 11.15. 12.7. 1 Sam. 10.17.\x*\nd* eMizipa\x + 10.17. Josh. 11.3.\x*.
\p
\v 12 UJefitha wasethuma izithunywa enkosini yabantwana bakoAmoni esithi: Ngilani lawe ukuthi uze kimi ukulwa elizweni lami?
\v 13 Inkosi yabantwana bakoAmoni yasisithi kuzithunywa zikaJefitha: Ngoba uIsrayeli wathatha ilizwe lami ekwenyukeni kwakhe eGibhithe\x + Nani 21.26. Dute. 2.19. Dute. 3.11. Josh. 13.25.\x* kusukela eArinoni\x + Nani 21.13.\x* kuze kube seJaboki kuze kube seJordani\x + Gen. 32.22.\x*; ngakho-ke libuyiseni ngokuthula.
\v 14 UJefitha wasephinda ethuma izithunywa futhi enkosini yabantwana bakoAmoni
\v 15 wathi kuye: Utsho njalo uJefitha: UIsrayeli kalithathanga ilizwe lakoMowabi lelizwe labantwana bakoAmoni\x + Dute. 2.9,19.\x*,
\v 16 kodwa ekwenyukeni kwabo besuka eGibhithe uIsrayeli wahamba edabula enkangala waya eLwandle oluBomvu\x + Nani 14.25. Dute. 1.40.\x*, wafika eKadeshi\x + Nani 13.26.\x*.
\v 17 UIsrayeli wasethuma izithunywa enkosini yeEdoma esithi: Ake sedlule sidabule elizweni lakho\x + Nani 20.14.\x*; kodwa inkosi yeEdoma kayilalelanga. Wathumela njalo enkosini yakoMowabi, kodwa kayivumanga\x + Nani 20.18-21.\x*. Ngakho uIsrayeli wahlala eKadeshi\x + Nani 20.1. Dute. 1.46.\x*.
\v 18 Basebedabula enkangala, balibhoda ilizwe leEdoma lelizwe lakoMowabi\x + Nani 21.4. Dute. 2.1-8.\x*, bafika lapho eliphuma khona ilanga kwelizwe lakoMowabi\x + Nani 21.11.\x*. Bamisa inkamba ngaphetsheya kweArinoni, kodwa kabangenanga emngceleni wakoMowabi, ngoba iArinoni yayingumngcele wakoMowabi\x + Nani 21.13. 22.36.\x*.
\v 19 UIsrayeli wasethuma izithunywa kuSihoni inkosi yamaAmori, inkosi yeHeshiboni\x + Nani 21.21. Dute. 2.26.\x*; uIsrayeli wathi kuye: Ake sedlule elizweni lakho siye endaweni yami\x + Nani 21.22. Dute. 2.27.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa uSihoni kamthembanga uIsrayeli ukuthi adlule emngceleni wakhe; kodwa uSihoni wabutha bonke abantu bakhe\x + Nani 21.23. Dute. 2.32.\x*, wamisa inkamba eJahazi, walwa loIsrayeli\x + Josh. 13.18.\x*.
\v 21 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, yanikela uSihoni labo bonke abantu bakhe esandleni sikaIsrayeli, babatshaya. Ngakho uIsrayeli wadla ilifa lelizwe lonke lamaAmori, abahlali balelolizwe\x + Nani 21.24,25. Dute. 2.33,34.\x*.
\v 22 Badla ilifa layo yonke imingcele yamaAmori kusukela eArinoni kuze kube seJaboki, njalo kusukela enkangala kuze kube seJordani\x + 11.13,26. Dute. 2.36.\x*.
\v 23 Khathesi-ke iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, yawaxotsha elifeni amaAmori phambi kwabantu bayo uIsrayeli; kanti wena uzakudla ilifa lalo yini?
\v 24 Kawuyikudla yini ilifa lalokhu uKemoshi unkulunkulu wakho akunika ukudla ilifa lakho\x + Nani 21.29.\x*? Ngakho loba ngubani iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu ezamxotsha elifeni phambi kwethu, lokhu sizakudla ilifa lakho\x + Dute. 9.5. 18.12. Josh. 3.10. Eks. 15. 9.\x*.
\v 25 Pho-ke wena ungcono yini okwedlula uBalaki indodana kaZipori inkosi yakoMowabi? Wake waxabana loIsrayeli; kumbe wake walwa labo yini\x + Nani 22.2. Dute. 23.3,4. Josh. 24.9.\x*;
\v 26 lapho uIsrayeli esehlala eHeshiboni lemizaneni yayo\x + Nani 21.25. Nani 32.37.\x*, leAroweri lemizaneni yayo, lakuyo yonke imizi esekhunjini lweArinoni\x + Dute. 2.36.\x*, iminyaka engamakhulu amathathu? Kungani-ke ungayophulanga ngalesosikhathi\x + Seb. 13.20. 1 Kho. 6.1.\x*?
\v 27 Ngakho mina kangonanga kuwe, kodwa wena wenza okubi kimi ngokulwa lami; iN\nd kosi\nd* uMahluleli kahlulele lamuhla phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli labantwana bakoAmoni\x + Gen. 16.5. 18.25.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa inkosi yabantwana bakoAmoni kayilalelanga amazwi kaJefitha awathumela kuyo.
\p
\v 29 UMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* wasesiza phezu kukaJefitha, wedlula eGileyadi leManase, wedlula eMizipa yeGileyadi; esuka eMizipa wedlulela kubantwana bakoAmoni\x + 3.10.\x*.
\v 30 UJefitha wafunga isifungo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni wathi: Uba uzanikela lokunikela abantwana bakoAmoni esandleni sami\x + Gen. 28.20. Nani 30.3. 1 Sam. 1.11.\x*,
\v 31 kuzakuthi loba yikuphi okuphuma eminyango yendlu yami ukungihlangabeza ekubuyeni kwami ngokuthula ngivela kubantwana bakoAmoni, kuzakuba ngokweN\nd kosi\x + Levi 27.2, 3.\x*\nd*, ngizakunikela kube ngumnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Hlab. 66.13.\x*.
\v 32 Ngakho uJefitha wasesedlulela ebantwaneni bakoAmoni ukulwa emelene labo; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasibanikela esandleni sakhe.
\v 33 Wasebatshaya kusukela eAroweri\x + Dute. 2.36.\x* uze ufike eMinithi\x + Hez. 27.17.\x*, imizi engamatshumi amabili, kuze kube seAbeli-Keramimi, ukutshaya okukhulukazi. Ngokunjalo abantwana bakoAmoni behliselwa phansi phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\s Indodakazi kaJefitha
\p
\v 34 UJefitha wasefika eMizipa endlini yakhe\x + 11.11.\x*. Khangela-ke, indodakazi yakhe yaphuma ukumhlangabeza\x + 1 Sam. 18.6.\x*, ilezigujana, lemigido; yayiyiyo yodwa eyakhe; ngaphandle kwayo wayengelandodana lendodakazi\x + Eks. 15.20. Jer. 31.4.\x*.
\v 35 Kwasekusithi lapho eyibona wadabula izigqoko zakhe wathi\x + Gen. 44.13.\x*: Maye ndodakazi yami! Ungithobisile kakhulu, njalo wena uphakathi kwabangihluphayo, ngoba mina ngivule umlomo wami eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ngingeke ngibuyele emuva\x + 21.18. Nani 30.2.\x*.
\v 36 Yasisithi kuye: Baba, uvulile umlomo wakho eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, yenza kimi njengalokho okuphume emlonyeni wakho, lokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* ikuphindisele ezitheni zakho, ebantwaneni bakoAmoni.
\v 37 Yasisithi kuyise: Akungenzele linto: Ngiyekela inyanga ezimbili, ngiye ngehle ezintabeni, ngililele ubuntombi bami, mina labangane bami\x + Eks. 4.26.\x*.
\v 38 Wasesithi: Hamba. Waseyiyekela ihamba inyanga ezimbili. Yasihamba, yona labangane bayo, yalilela ubuntombi bayo ezintabeni.
\v 39 Kwasekusithi ekupheleni kwenyanga ezimbili yabuyela kuyise, owenza kuyo isifungo sakhe asifungayo; yona kayiyazanga indoda. Kwasekusiba ngumkhuba koIsrayeli:
\v 40 Iminyaka ngeminyaka amadodakazi akoIsrayeli ayehamba uku\add ya\add*khumbula indodakazi kaJefitha umGileyadi insuku ezine ngomnyaka\x + 11.31.\x*.
